Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I close my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:30.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hear the waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:32.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I see the deep\Nblue of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:38.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Filled with the scent of\Nsummer that never ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,in these hollow,\Ndrifting days...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:58.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,met that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,with eyes like the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,... I dont wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, heading out, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Big broooother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait for meee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:46.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Dad and Mom are waiting too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be\Nhot again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm stopping by\Nthe convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll grab a drink too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sad things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Painful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:22.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,These are all that come\Nto mind when it arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I wish that summer would just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,end already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just now, I think something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,was in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A fish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It looked too big, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,the deep sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so clear and pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Her eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's fine to let yourself be\Ncaptivated by the sea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:34.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you lean out that\Nfar, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:40.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's not like I was going\Nto fall into the sea or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My apologies then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She is totally strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I honestly thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You were about\Nto throw yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please, at least you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,but don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did I offend you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning, Miko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry I couldn't walk\Nwith you this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:55.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Overslept?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep without hanging\Nmy uniform to dry yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I had to dry it\Nwith a hairdryer—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I seriously thought\NI wouldn't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:10.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your cold's still not gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No worries, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Forget me, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Were you okay on your own this morning!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You didn't get hassled\Nby any weirdos, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko's at it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko is seriously so\Noverprotective of Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Come on—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako's so clumsy,\NI worry about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just the other day, she\Ntripped over nothing at all—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:45.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she does\Ntrip over thin air a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I just can't\Nleave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I kinda get where\NMiko's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Exactly, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning—get back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,it's been sunk at the\Nbottom of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why is it that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,would think of that\Nperson as the sea...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did I feel that way...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you watch Mikarin's video?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I did, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We've got section\Npractice today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah... hope I can play well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Crap! I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Student council announcement:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:05.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Today's council meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,will begin at 4:45 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinaaaako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can we stop by the\Nbookstore on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And the convenience store\Ntoo! There's a new dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mikooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Glad, I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:23.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takano from the Math\Nclass says we have to finish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:29.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,worksheets to make up for his missed class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I was gonna hang out with Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:37.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Yamashita says once you're done,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,report to the guidance office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,H-Hinakooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna gooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate worksheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:54.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And Yamashita's totally\Ngonna chew me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you don't go, it'll just\Nget worse, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you\Ntill you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:03.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then I'll finish it in seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Make the skirt longer too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The choker too! Off with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hinako—wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:32.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I need to kill some\Ntime somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to\Ndo in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the library...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,read a book until\NMiko-chan gets here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The smell of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard the sound\Nof the waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's... from this morning—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What am I even doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Still wearing my indoor shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I should go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:40.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan might\Nbe done already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Fou... nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Fou... nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ahh... such a lovely scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:41.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was worth coming all the\Nway from the West Sea Route.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:48.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was interrupted this morning,\Nbut now I can finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:57.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you it was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Y-you... are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You wretch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why is a mermaid here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How dare you interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's my prey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Stay behind me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A lowly sea hag like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mermaid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sea hag...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Such a lowly creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,talking big, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is... mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was like──
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A scene straight out of hell──
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So gruesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even move a finger—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:12.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've been searching\Nfor you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Searching...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,came here to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:39.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your blood and flesh are\Nexceptionally delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why those vulgar\Nfools gather around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My heart pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Without knowing the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Like the roar of the tide—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'll become even more\Ndelicious from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In these empty\Ndays, filled with the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:06.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,scent of an endless,\Nunseen summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If it's this person who\Nappeared so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She might...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:38.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:53.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why!? Why\Nare you soaking wet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,after that, I probably\Ncaused a lot of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,her cold came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan may not look like,\Nbut she's got a weak Body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't that rude!? {Says the same thing as in the sign here}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hope it doesn't get worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's going\Nto be hot again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Shall we go to the\Nsea after school~?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If we go, we should\Neat something first...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'd eat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it really true...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,ah, but I won't eat you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Make sure you treat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,that wound properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wa... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:07.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako? You here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:14.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hii-na-kooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:17.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Heyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:22.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,About me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:45.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said you'd eat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why... yesterday...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,take your seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,oh, before homeroom, we've
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,got a transfer\Nstudent to introduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The tide...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:18.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She'll be joining this\Nclass starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The smell of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is Shiori Oumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:35.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I came here to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This person might...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:44.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,fulfill my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She might...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:57.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,let me die...
